    "code": "012", 
    "data": "Dua-e-Ahad\nIt is narrated from Hazrat Imam Jaffer Sadiq (a.s.) that whoever recites the following ‘Dua-e-Ahad’ for 40 days after namaz-e-subah (morning prayer), he will be included amongst the companion of Sahebul-Asr-e-waz-Zaman (a.s.). If he dies before the occulation of the Imam (a.s.), Allah (s.w.t.) will raise him from the grave so that he can be with the Imam (a.s.). Allah (s.w.t.) will give him reward (sawab) of 1000 good deeds for each word of this dua and his 1000 sins will be forgiven.\nبِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ \nBISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM\nIn the name of Allah, the Beneficent, the Merciful.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ رَبَّ النُّوْرِ الْعَظِيْمِ وَرَبَّ الْكُرْسِىِّ الرَّفِيْعِ \nALLAAHUMMA RABBAN NOORIL A’ZEEM WA RABBAL KURSIYYIR RAFEE-E’ \nO Allah! Lord of the Great Light, Lord of the Elevated Throne, \nوَرَبَّ الْبَحْرِ الْمَسْجُوْرِ وَمُنْزِلَ التَّوْرٰيةِ وَالْاِنْجِيْلِ وَالزَّبُوْرِ \nWA RABBAL BAHRIL MASJOORE WA MUNZELAT TAWRAATE WAL INJEELE WAZ ZABOORE \nLord of the tumultuous seas, and the revealer of the Tawrah, Injeel, and Zaboor, \nوَرَبَّ الظِّلِّ وَالْحَرُوْرِ وَمُنْزِلَ الْقُرْاٰنِ الْعَظِيْمِ \nWA RABBAZ ZILLE WAL HAROORE WA MUNZELAL QUR-AANIL A’ZEEME \nLord of the shadows and the warmth’s, And the revealer of the Great Quran. \nوَرَبَّ الْمَلٰٓئِكَةِ الْمُقَرَّبِيْنَ وَالْاَنْبِيَآءِ وَالْمُرْسَلِيْنَ \nWA RABBAL MALAAA-EKATIL MOQARRABEENA WAL AMBEYAAA-E WAL MURSALEENA \nLord of the proximate angels and prophets and messengers.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّىْ اَسْئَلُكَ بِوَجْهِكَ الْكَرِيْمِ وَبِنُوْرِ وَجْهِكَ الْمُنِيْرِ \nALLAAHUMMA INNEE AS-ALOKA BE-WAJHEKAL KAREEME WA BE-NOORE WAJHEKAL MONEERE \nO Allah! I beseech thee, for the sake of Your Nobel Visage. And for the sake of Your Enlightening Visage,\nوَبِمُلْكِكَ الْقَدِيْمِ يَا حَىُّ يَا قَيُّوْمُ اَسْئَلُكَ بِاسْمِكَ الَّذِىْ \nWA MULKEKAL QADEEME YAA HAYYO YAA QAYYOOMO AS-ALOKA BISMEKAL LAZEE \nand Your ever existing kingdom. O Ever Living! O Controller! I beseech Thee in Your Name \nاَشْرَقَتْ بِهٖ السَّمٰوَاتُ وَالْاَرْضُوْنَ \nASHRAQAT BEHIS SAMAAWAATO WAL ARAZOONA \nwhich lits the heavens and the earths; \nوَبِاسْمِكَ الَّذِىْ يَصْلَحُ بِهٖ الْاَوَّلُوْنَ وَالْآخِرُوْنَ \nWA BISMEKAL LAZEE YASLAHO BEHIL AWWALOONA WAL AAKHEROONA \nand in Your Name, by which the ancient and the latter ones become upright. \nيَا حَيًّا قَبْلَ كُلِّ حَىٍّ وَيَا حَيًّا بَعْدَ كُلِّ حَىٍّ \nYAA HAYYAN QABLA KULLE HAYYIN WA YAA HAYYAN BA’-DA KULLE HA’YYIN \nO Ever living who has before every living being. O Ever Living Who shall (exist) after every living being. \nوَيَا حَيًّا حِيْنَ لاَ حَىَّ يَا مُحْيِىَ الْمَوْتٰى وَمُمِيْتَ الْاَحْيَآءِ يَا حَىُّ لاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اَنْتَ \nWA YAA HAYYAN HEENA LAA HAYYA YAA MOHYEYAL MAWTAA WA MOMEETAL AHYAAA-E YAA HAYYO LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTA\nO Ever Living Who existed when there was no life. O Giver of life to dead. O One Who causes death to the living one. O Ever Living. There is no god except Thou. \nاَللّٰهُمَّ بَلِّغْ مَوْلاَنَا الْاِمَامَ الْهَادِىَ الْمَهْدِىَّ الْقَآئِمَ بِاَمْرِكَ \nALLAAHUMMA BALLIGH MAWLAANA EMAAMAL HAADEYAL MAHDIYYAL QAAA-EMA BE-AMREKA \nO Allah! Send our master the leader, the guide, the guided, the upriser with Your command. \nصَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْهِ وَعَلٰى اٰبَآئِهِ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ \nSALAWAATULLAAHE A’LAYHE WA A’LAA AABAAA-EHIT TAAHEREEN \nBlessings of Allah be on him and his pure forefathers \nعَنْ جَمِيْعِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ فِىْ مَشَارِقِ الْاَرْضِ وَمَغَارِبِهَا \nA’N JAMEEL-I’L MOMINEENA WAL MOMINAATE FEE MASHAAREQIL ARZE WA MAGHAAREBEHAA \nfrom all the believing men and believing women. In the easts of the earth and it’s wests, \nسَهْلِهَا وَجَبَلِهَا وَبَرِّهَا وَبَحْرِهَا وَعَنِّىْ وَعَنْ وَالِدَىَّ مِنَ الصَّلَوَاتِ \nSAHLEHAA WA JABALEHAA WA BARREHAA WA BAHREHAA WA A’NNEE WA A’N WAALEDAYYA MENAS SALAWAATE \nin its plains and its mountains, its lands and its seas, from me and my parents. Blessings, \nزِنَةَ عَرْشِ اللهِ وَمِدَادَ كَلِمَاتِهٖ وَمَا اَحْصَاهُ عِلْمُهٗ وَاَحَاطَ بِهٖ كِتَابُهٗ \nZENATA A’RSHILLAAHE WA MEDAADA KALEMAATEHI WA MAA AHSAAHO I’LMOHU WA AHAATA BEHI KETAABOHU \nwhich are the weight of Allah’s throne and ink of His words, and whatever His knowledge enumerates and His book encompasses. \nاَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّىْ اُجَدِّدُ لَهٗ فِىْ صَبِيْحَةِ يَوْمِىْ هٰذَا وَمَا عِشْتُ مِنْ اَيَّامِىْ عَهْدً ا\nALLAAHUMMA INNEE OJADDEDO LAHU FEE SABEEHATE YAWMEE HAAZAA WA MAA I’SHTO MIN AYYAAMEE A’HDAN \nO Allah! Renew for him my covenant, pledge \nوَعَقْدًا وَبَيْعَةً لَهٗ فِىْ عُنُقِىْ لاَ اَحُوْلُ عَنْهَا وَلاَ اَزُوْلُ اَبَدًا \nWA A’QDAN WA BAY-A’TAN LAHU FEE O’NOQEE LAA AHULO A’NHAA WA LAA AZOOLO ABADAN \nand allegiance on my neck in the morning of this day of mine and whatever days (of my life) I live. I shall never turn away from it nor let it ever vanish. \nاَللّٰهُمَّ اجْعَلْنِىْ مِنْ اَنْصَارِهٖ وَاَعْوَانِهٖ وَالذَّابِّيْنَ عَنْهُ \nALLAAHUMMAJ-A’LNEE MIN ANSAAREHI WA AA’-WAANEHI WAZ-ZAAAB-BEENA A’NHO \nO Allah! Appoint me among his helpers, aides, and his protectors. \nوَالْمُسَارِعِيْنَ اِلَيْهِ فِىْ قَضَآءِ حَوَآئِجِهٖ وَالْمُمْتَثِلِيْنَ لِاَوَامِرِهٖ \nWAL MOSAARE-E’ENA ELAYHE FEE QAZAAA-E HAWAA-EJEHEE WAL MUMTASLEENA LE-AWAAMEREHI \nThose who hasten to fulfill his commands and obey his orders. \nوَالْمُحَامِيْنَ عَنْهُ وَالسَّابِقِيْنَ اِلٰى اِرَادَتِهٖ وَالْمُسْتَشْهَدِيْنَ بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ \nWAL MOHAAMMEENA A’NHO WAS SAABEQEENA ELAA ERAADATEHI WAL MUSTASH-HADEENA BAYNA YADAYHE \nThose who are his supporters and compete with each other to (fulfill) his intention and seek martyrdom in his presence. \nاَللّٰهُمَّ اِنْ حَالَ بَيْنِىْ وَبَيْنَهُ الْمَوْتُ الَّذِىْ جَعَلْتَهٗ عَلٰى عِبَادِكَ \nALLAAHUMMA IN HAALA BAYNEE WA BAYNAHUL MAWTUL LAZEE JA-A’LTAHU A’LAA E’BAADEKA \nO Allah! If death occurs between me and him (before the reappearance) (death) which you have made obligatory and decreed for your servants, \nحَتْمًا مَّقْضِيًّا فَاَخْرِجْنِىْ مِنْ قِبْرِىْ مُؤْتَزِرًا كَفَنِىْ شَاهِرًا سَيْفِىْ \nHATMAN MAQZIYYAN FA-AKHRIJNEE MIN QABREE MOA-TAZERAN KAFANEE SHAAHERAN SAYFEE \nthen raise me from my grave, wrapped in my shroud, my sword unsheathed, \nمُجَرِّدًا قَنَاتِىْ مُلَبِّيًا دَعْوَةَ الدَّاعِىْ فِى الْحَاضِرِ وَالْبَادِىْ \nMOJARREDAN QANAATEE MOLABBEYAN DAA’-WATAD DAA-E’E FIL HAAZERE WAL BAADEE \nmy spear bared, answering the call of the caller in cities as well as deserts. \nاَللّٰهُمَّ اَرِنِى الطَّلْعَةَ الرَّشيْدَةَ وَالْغُرَّةَ الْحَمِيْدَةَ \nALLAAHUMMA ARENIT TAL-A’TAR RASHEEDATA WAL GHURRATAL HAMEEDATA \nO Allah! Show me the rightly guided face of (Imam a.s.), the praiseworthy moon (referring to the face of Imam a.s.) \nوَاكْحُلْ نَاظِرِىْ بِنَظْرَةٍ مِّنِّىْ اِلَيْهِ وَعَجِّلْ فرَجَهٗ \nWAK-HUL NAAZEREE BE-NAZRATIN MINNEE ELAYHE WA A’JJIL FARAJAHU \nand enlighten my vision by looking at him. And hasten his reappearance, make his arrival smooth, \nوَسَهِّلْ مَخْرَجَهٗ وَ اَوْسِعْ مَنْهَجَهٗ وَاسْلُكْ بِىْ مَحَجَّتَهٗ \nWA SAHHIL MAKHRAJAHU WA AWSEA’-MANHAJAHU WASLUK BEE MAHAJJATAHU \nvasten his path, make me tread on his way \nوَاَنْفِذْ اَمْرَهٗ وَاشْدُدْ اَزْرَهٗ وَاعْمُرِ اللّٰهُمَّ بِهٖ بِلاَدَكَ وَاَحْىِ بِهٖ عِبَادَكَ \nWANFIZ AMRAHU WASHDUD AZRAHU WA’-MURIL LAAHUMMA BEHI BELAADAKA WA AHYE BEHI E’BAADAKA \nand implement his authority and strengthen his back. O Allah! Inhabit Your cities through him and give life to Your servants \nفَاِنَّكَ قُلْتَ وَقَوْلُكَ الْحَقُّ ظَهَرَ الْفَسَادُ فِىْ الْبَرِّ وَالْبَحْرِ \nFA-INNAKA QULTA WA QAWLOKAL HAQQO ZAHARAL FASAADO FIL BARRE WAL BAHRE \ndue to him for surely You have said and Your word is truth, “Corruption will become rampant in land and on sea \nبِمَا كَسَبَتْ اَيْدِى النَّاسِ فَاَظْهِرِ اللّٰهُمَّ لَنَا وَلِيَّكَ وَابْنَ بِنْتِ نَبِيِّكَ \nBEMAA KASABAT AYDIN NAASE FA-AZHERILLAAHUMMA LANAA WALIYYAKA WABNA BINTE NABIYYEKAL \nbecause of the evil which men’s hand have earned” Then O Allah! Manifest for us Your slave and the son of Your Prophet’s daughter, \nالْمُسَمّٰى بِاسْمِ رَسُوْلِكَ حَتّٰى لاَ يَظْفَرَ بِشَىْءٍ مِّنَ الْبَاطِلِ اِلاَّ مَزَّقَهٗ \nMOSAMMAA BISME RASOOLEKA HATTA LAA YAZFARA BESHAY-IN MENAL BAATELE ILLAA MAZZAQAHU \nwhose name is the same as that of Your messenger, so that nothing from falsehood is victorious except that he tears them (falsehood) to pieces, \nوَيُحِقَّ الْحَقَّ وَيُحَقِّقَهٗ وَاجْعَلْهُ اللّٰهُمَّ مَفْزَعًا لِمَظْلُوْمِ عِبَادِكَ \nWA YOHIQQAL HAQQA WA YOHAQQEQAHU WAJ-A’LHUL LAAHUMMA MAFZA-A’N LE-MAZLOOME E’BAADEKA \nestablishes the truth and the truth confirms him. And O Allah! Appoint him as a refuge for Your oppressed servants \nوَ نَاصِرًا لِمَنْ لاَ يَجِدُ لَهٗ نَاصِرًا غَيْرَكَ وَمُجَدِّدًا لِمَا عُطِّلَ مِنْ اَحْكَامِ كِتَابِكَ \nWA NAASERAN LEMAN LAA YAJEDO LAHOO NAASERAN GHAYRAKA WA MOJADDEDAN LEMAA U’TTELA MIN AHKAAME KETAABEKA \nand a helper for the one who does not find any helper for himself except You and the renewer of all the laws of Your book \nوَ مُشَيِّدًا لِمَا وَرَدَ مِنْ اَعْلاَمِ دِيْنِكَ وَسُنَنِ نَبِيِّكَ \nWA MOSHAYYEDAN LEMAA WARADA MIN AA’-LAAME DEENEKA WA SONANE NABIYYEKA \nwhich have been tampered with and the rebuilder of the science of Your religion and the traditions of Your Prophet \nصَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَآلِهٖ وَاجْعَلْهُ اللّٰهُمَّ مِمَّنْ حَصَّنْتَهٗ مِنْ بَاْسِ الْمُعْتَدِيْنَ \nSALLALLAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI WAJ-A’LHUL LAAHUMMA MIMMAN HASSANTAHU MIN BAASIL MOA’TADEENA \n(peace of Allah be on him and his progeny) and O Allah! Make him among those whom you have protected from the evils of the adversaries. \nاَللّٰهُمَّ وَ سُرَّ نَبِيَّكَ مُحَمَّدًا صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَاٰلِهٖ بِرُؤْيَتِهٖ \nALLAAHUMMA WA SURRA NABIYYAKA SALLALLAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI BE-ROAYATEHI \nO Allah! And provide joy to Your Prophet Mohammed (peace be on him and his progeny) by his vision \nوَمَنْ تَبِعَهٗ عَلٰى دَعْوَتِهٖ وَارْحَمِ اسْتِكَانَتَنَا بَعْدَهٗ \nWA MAN TABE-A’HU A’LAA DA’-WATEHI WARHAMIS- TAKAANATANAA BA’-DAHU \nand (the vision of) the one who follows him on his call and have mercy on our poverty after his arrival \nاَللّٰهُمَّ اكْشِفْ هٰذِهِ الْغُمَّةَ عَنْ هٰذِهِ الْاُمَّةِ بِحُضُوْرِهٖ \nALLAAHUMMAK-SHIF HAAZEHIL GHUMMATA A’N HAAZEHIL UMMATE BE-HOZOOREHI \nO Allah! Remove his sorrow (of occultation) from this nation with his presence \nوَعَجِّلْ لَنَا ظُهُوْرَهٗ اِنَّهُمْ يَرَوْنَهٗ بَعِيْدًا وَّنَرٰيهُ قَرِيْبًا \nWA A’JJIL LANAA ZOHOORAHU INNAHUM YARAWNAHU BA-E’EDAN WA NARAAHO QAREEBAN \nand hasten for us his reappearance. They (the disbelievers) consider it to be distant while we consider it to be near. \nبِرَحْمَتِكَ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ.\nBE-RAHMATEKA YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEENA.\nFor the sake of Your mercy, O the most Merciful of all Mercifuls. \nThen strike your hand on your thice 3 times and say’.\nاَلْعَجَلَ الْعَجَلَ يَا مَوْلاىَ يَا صَاحِبَ الزَّمَانِ.\nAL-A’JAL AL-A’JAL YAA MAWLAAYA YAA SAAHEBAZ ZAMAANE\nHasten! Hasten! O my Master, O Master of the era.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    ", 
    "title": "Dua e Ahad"
}